    "# 📊 Vortex Tech Internship 2026\n",
    "# Week 2: Exploratory Data Analysis (EDA)\n",
    "**Dataset:** Super Store Sales"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "7173137a",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## Objective\n",
    "Perform exploratory data analysis to discover meaningful patterns using visualizations, feature engineering and business insights."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "id": "21533099",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "import pandas as pd\n",
    "import numpy as np\n",
    "import matplotlib.pyplot as plt\n",
    "import seaborn as sns\n",
    "sns.set_style('whitegrid')\n",
    "plt.rcParams['figure.figsize']=(10,6)\n",
    "\n",
    "df=pd.read_csv('/content/super store(2).csv')\n",
    "df.head()"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "01743bf9",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## Data Recap"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "id": "957d30b5",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "display(df.head())\n",
    "display(df.info())\n",
    "display(df.describe(include='all'))\n",
    "print(df.isnull().sum())\n",
    "print(\"Duplicates:\",df.duplicated().sum())\n",
    "df.drop_duplicates(inplace=True)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "67d680a4",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## Feature Engineering"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "id": "0bec3061",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "df['Order Date']=pd.to_datetime(df['Order Date'])\n",
    "df['Ship Date']=pd.to_datetime(df['Ship Date'])\n",
    "df['Shipping Days']=(df['Ship Date']-df['Order Date']).dt.days\n",
    "df['Order Month']=df['Order Date'].dt.month\n",
    "df['Order Year']=df['Order Date'].dt.year\n",
    "df.head()"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "57e3df0c",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## Correlation Heatmap"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "id": "ddf8e8e5",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    df['Order Date'] = pd.to_datetime(df['Order Date'], dayfirst=True)
df['Ship Date'] = pd.to_datetime(df['Ship Date'], dayfirst=True)

df['Order Month'] = df['Order Date'].dt.month
df['Order Year'] = df['Order Date'].dt.year
df['Shipping Days'] = (df['Ship Date'] - df['Order Date']).dt.days

corr=df[['Sales','Shipping Days','Order Month','Order Year']].corr(numeric_only=True)
plt.figure(figsize=(6,5))
sns.heatmap(corr,annot=True,cmap='coolwarm')
plt.title('Correlation Heatmap')
plt.show()
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "339b431a",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "**Observation:** Correlation is explored among engineered numeric variables and Sales."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "77ce4aee",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## Scatter Plot: Sales vs Shipping Days"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "id": "b0407470",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "sns.scatterplot(data=df,x='Shipping Days',y='Sales')\n",
    "plt.title('Sales vs Shipping Days')\n",
    "plt.show()"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "170e7c6f",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "**Insight:** Examine whether longer shipping duration is associated with higher-value orders."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "ac5fc657",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## Monthly Sales Trend"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "id": "de00267b",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "monthly=df.groupby('Order Month')['Sales'].sum().reset_index()\n",
    "sns.lineplot(data=monthly,x='Order Month',y='Sales',marker='o')\n",
    "plt.title('Monthly Sales Trend')\n",
    "plt.show()"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "5f31754d",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "**Insight:** Sales fluctuate across months, indicating seasonality."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "75aefdf1",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## Sales by Category"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "id": "14942081",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "tmp=df.groupby('Category')['Sales'].sum().reset_index()\n",
    "sns.barplot(data=tmp,x='Category',y='Sales')\n",
    "plt.title('Total Sales by Category')\n",
    "plt.xticks(rotation=25)\n",
    "plt.show()"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "68003f76",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "**Insight:** Compare overall sales contribution across categorys."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "ccfbf727",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
